    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been kept in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a flawless exterior with deep, mirror-like paint and zero imperfections. The interior is equally immaculate, featuring pristine leather seats with no creasing, a spotless headliner, and that signature new-car scent. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates perfectly, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a non-smoker, no-accident, showroom-quality example that satisfies even the most discerning inspection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
